infmon (0.0.1~unreleased-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Added: Debian packaging tree (`debian/`) producing three binary `.deb`s
    (`infmon-backend`, `infmon-frontend`, `infmon-cli`) plus an `infmon` meta
    package, per spec 008.
  * Added: systemd unit `infmon-frontend.service` (Type=notify, hardened,
    `PartOf=vpp.service`).
  * Added: Maintainer scripts that strictly leave VPP alone on install,
    upgrade, remove, and purge.
  * Added: `tools/sync-debian-changelog.py`: regenerates `debian/changelog`
    from this file at source-package build time.
  * Added: GitHub Actions workflow `package-deb.yml`: cross-builds the `.deb`s
    for `arm64` on every push and uploads them as workflow artefacts.

 -- InFMon maintainers <r12f.code@gmail.com>  Thu, 01 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000
